cpu
1:emon 收集指标
  INST_RETIRED.ANY/CPU_CLK_UNHALTED.THREAD/CPU_CLK_UNHALTED.REF_TSC
  metric_CPU utilization %/metric_CPU utilization% in kernel mode/metric_CPU operating frequency (in GHz)
  metric_CPI/metric_kernel_CPI
  metric_L2 MPI (includes code+data+rfo w/ prefetches) /metric_LLC MPI (includes code+data+rfo w/ prefetches)
  metric_Average LLC demand data read miss latency (in ns)
  metric_NUMA %_Reads addressed to local DRAM / metric_NUMA %_Reads addressed to remote DRAM
  metric_memory bandwidth read (MB/sec) /metric_memory bandwidth write (MB/sec) /metric_memory bandwidth total (MB/sec)
  从不同硬件角度：整个系统/socket/core/thread 角度去展示以上信息

